      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. This car is absolutely pristine\u2014it's been my pride and joy and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. You really have to see it in person to believe it. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
